sentences.english: The provisional regulations on the registration of immovable property were officially implemented.
sentences.chinese: 不动产登记暂行条例正式实施。

sentences.english: The Interim Regulations were uniformly implemented throughout China.
sentences.chinese: 暂行条例在全中国统一实施。

sentences.english: I. Earnestly making all preparations for the implementation of the Interim Measures.
sentences.chinese: 认真做好《暂行办法》实施的各项准备工作。

sentences.english: The new provisional regulations for tax on farmland used for nonagricultural purposes and detailed rules for their implementation were instituted.
sentences.chinese: 执行新的耕地占用税暂行条例及其实施细则。

sentences.english: Article 27 of the Interim Regulations on the Supervision and Administration of State-owned Assets of Enterprises shall be deleted.
sentences.chinese: 删去《企业国有资产监督管理暂行条例》第二十七条。

sentences.english: The following is the provisional rules of arbitration procedure of the foreign trade arbitration commission.
sentences.chinese: 下面是对外贸易仲裁委员会仲裁程序暂行规定。

sentences.english: The use of the documents on fined or confiscated money shall conform to the interim provisions for the administration of fine documents.
sentences.chinese: 罚没款票据的使用，应当符合罚款票据管理暂行规定。

sentences.english: Article 17 of the Interim Measures on the Administration of Cable Televisions.
sentences.chinese: 《有线电视管理暂行办法》第十七条。

sentences.english: Provisional Rules of Preventing Coast Water Pollution of the P. C. C.
sentences.chinese: 中华人民共和国防止沿海水域污染暂行规定。
